title: Unreal: Return to Na Pali (Easy) [22:37] (RTA)
description: The Unreal expansion! Pretty fun run, it's basically a little baby version of Unreal :D This is actually faster than the first segmented run of the game. There's another segmented run that's 20:55, so maybe I'll try to get close to that. Shout outs to TooManyMyths for running the game in RTA and telling me to run the game.
